data.description: This 4-bedroom CBS home in Port St. Lucie is move-in ready with modern upgrades. The kitchen boasts a Whirlpool stainless refrigerator, GE convection oven/stove, and a GE/Whirlpool washer/dryer set, all 3 years old. The property features a 3-ton TRANE A/C with a UV system (4 years old) and a new AO Smith electric hot water heater (installed 1/2024). Outside, the roof is solar-ready, and the fenced backyard has room for a pool and spa. A well serves the sprinkler system (4 years old), and metal accordion hurricane shutters provide storm protection (2019). The home includes a 2-car garage with a new LiftMaster opener. Tile flooring throughout adds a modern touch. Conveniently located near the Turnpike, this home is an ideal blend of comfort and convenience.
